title: Urgent appeal to trace missing pregnant mum and five-year-old daughter
text:
Have you seen missing Alicja and five-year-old daughter? Credit: West Yorkshire Police West Yorkshire Police are asking a heavily pregnant woman to get in touch after she was reported missing with her five-year-old daughter.
Alicja Dworakowska and her daughter, who are from the Beeston area of Leeds, were last heard from on Monday.
The 29-year-old is heavily pregnant, with blonde-ginger, shoulder-length hair and freckles. She was wearing a black, water-repellent coat.
Her daughter is white with blonde hair and was wearing a pink hat, with earflaps, a beige coat and a pink dress.
"Alcija is urged to contact the police at the earliest opportunity. If you have any information on Alicja and her daughter's whereabouts please contact police as soon as possible on 101 and Quote: log 1018."
